sequenceDiagram
    actor Student
    participant Web as Flask Web App
    participant DB as PostgreSQL

    Student->>Web: Open course detail page
    Web->>DB: Read course and lessons
    DB-->>Web: Course data
    Web-->>Student: Display course details
    Student->>Web: Click Enroll
    Web->>DB: Insert enrollment
    Web->>DB: Insert progress rows for lessons
    DB-->>Web: Commit transaction
    Web-->>Student: Show learning page

